{"tid":1876774,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳曼娜不懼肺炎搞好友飯局 約胡楓家燕姐打邊爐：疫情不及友情深","createTime":"2020-02-12T15:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T15:57:19.000Z","uid":82938,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7b3670b3b6a013d8d73588acf52a06bd0b314f90","tid":1876774,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:20:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2562234/%E3%80%90%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%85%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%E3%80%91%E9%99%B3%E6%9B%BC%E5%A8%9C%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%BC%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%90%9E%E5%A5%BD%E5%8F%8B%E9%A3%AF%E5%B1%80%E3%80%80%E7%B4%84%E8%83%A1%E6%A5%93%E5%AE%B6%E7%87%95%E5%A7%90%E6%89%93%E9%82%8A%E7%88%90%EF%BC%9A%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8A%E5%8F%8B%E6%83%85%E6%B7%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2562234%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E5%25AE%2585%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%259B%25BC%25E5%25A8%259C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2587%25BC%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E6%2590%259E%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E5%258F%258B%25E9%25A3%25AF%25E5%25B1%2580%25E3%2580%2580%25E7%25B4%2584%25E8%2583%25A1%25E6%25A5%2593%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E7%2587%2595%25E5%25A7%2590%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%2582%258A%25E7%2588%2590%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%258F%258B%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%25B7%25B1&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GKDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=68f51386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2562234/%E3%80%90%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%85%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%E3%80%91%E9%99%B3%E6%9B%BC%E5%A8%9C%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%BC%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%90%9E%E5%A5%BD%E5%8F%8B%E9%A3%AF%E5%B1%80%E3%80%80%E7%B4%84%E8%83%A1%E6%A5%93%E5%AE%B6%E7%87%95%E5%A7%90%E6%89%93%E9%82%8A%E7%88%90%EF%BC%9A%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8A%E5%8F%8B%E6%83%85%E6%B7%B1</a><br />\n<br />\n新型冠狀病毒肺炎肆虐，有建議親友減少聚會免交叉感染。另外，早前有肺炎確診者與親人打邊爐及燒烤後，令參與的家族成員逾半數人確診感染武漢肺炎，令人對打邊爐有戒心。資深藝人陳曼娜近日邀來好友胡楓、黃百鳴、安德尊聚會，卻齊齊打邊爐盆菜宴，無懼邊爐可能是傳播病毒的源頭，陳曼娜更稱：「疫情不及友情深！」<br />\n<br />\n陳曼娜（Mann姐）在社交平台發布相片，一班好友如薛家燕、孫泳恩、黃百鳴、安德尊林建明、胡楓、何麗全夫婦等，跟Manna姐相約打邊爐兼食盆菜，相識多年知己把酒談天，兼作新年聚會。"},{"pid":"8641947c20fee955a431f11cc220f35628241efb","tid":1876774,"uid":82938,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:21:32.000Z","msg":"老人武漢全席"},{"pid":"734da9e12b5aafe824dfdeb37dc3f72347123b6a","tid":1876774,"uid":34071,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/11/13/fcCjoa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F11%2F13%2FfcCjoa.png&h=5b574de7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6ee37236dbe9590b6a499ac6c35ef1bf971f203","tid":1876774,"uid":74958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:22:46.000Z","msg":"有黃百嗚咁刺激？"},{"pid":"a82c8bf65dac6744db6a9e9ab4fe3f555f372762","tid":1876774,"uid":83328,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:23:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190411/ee0e01cb940747c2880ffa019d85f2f9.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20190411%2Fee0e01cb940747c2880ffa019d85f2f9.jpeg&h=6e44fba5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e3b0b2d31fc42ba4d8386b6a5c7367e901ce2aa","tid":1876774,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:23:20.000Z","msg":"邊爐家族"},{"pid":"29fae2e62008fd3d4b2c482aaa1d5178beff5f26","tid":1876774,"uid":79056,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:24:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WLgbopx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWLgbopx.jpg&h=cbc741a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"725db888fae9ef902e2d28b0a0e4a8b035dd880b","tid":1876774,"uid":140949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:24:58.000Z","msg":"幾好，咁啱隻中國武漢肺炎專殺廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm